{"tid":545677,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"世界最年長男人逝世 享嵩壽112歲又189天","createTime":"2018-01-30T17:55:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-31T06:00:22.000Z","uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f4970b01ee6bfee1673f82d6284b197b44f08e93","tid":545677,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T17:55:55.000Z","msg":"2018-01-31 00:03<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕西班牙男子弗朗西斯科&middot;努涅斯&middot;奧利韋拉（Francisco Nunez Olivera）29日晚間10時30分在家中安詳辭世，享嵩壽112歲又189天，他出生於1905年7月25日，他所居住的比恩韋尼達市鎮（Bienvenida）宣布這天將訂為紀念日。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpuWKIo0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpuWKIo0.jpg&h=c1fd5990&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">西班牙男子弗朗西斯科&middot;努涅斯&middot;奧利韋拉29日晚間10時30分在家中安詳辭世，享嵩壽112歲又189天。（圖擷取自每日郵報）</span><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpVGSJU2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpVGSJU2.jpg&h=c56940eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">市長安東尼奧&middot;卡梅納對他的逝世指出，「這是當地，甚至是全世界的遺憾」。（圖擷取自el periodico）</span><br />\n<br />\n根據英國《每日郵報》報導，弗朗西斯科將於30日安葬在家鄉巴達霍斯省（Badajoz）的比恩韋尼達市鎮，在去世時由女兒瑪麗亞&middot;安東尼（Maria Antonia）陪伴著他，市長安東尼奧&middot;卡梅納（Antonio Carmena）對此指出，「這是當地，甚至是全世界的遺憾」。<br />\n<br />\n安東尼奧表示，「近幾年來，他對我們意義重大，他代表我們的市鎮，使我們變得知名和受人歡迎」，「他是本市生活品質的最佳寫照，此處為無汙染的農村，擁有傳統生活、吳壓力的工作」，市長宣布將1月29日訂為弗朗西斯科紀念日。<br />\n<br />\n巴達霍斯省所隸屬的埃斯特雷馬杜拉自治區首長吉列爾莫&middot;費爾南德斯&middot;瓦拉（Guillermo Fern&aacute;ndez Vara）也在推特上發祭悼文，弗朗西斯科曾參加過第二次摩洛哥戰爭，他還擁有2名分別為97與93歲的手足、4個孩子、9個孫子與15個曾孫，家屬把他的長壽歸因於食用自種蔬菜，以及每日一杯紅葡萄酒。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2327696\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2327696&d=CEl7%2BMrVAOvvOxzybALzX8P%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=890d949f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2327696&h=caa3e9e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2327696</a>"},{"pid":"253e0940f78a1050ac2ce65ca1c6f96e00c0ef0f","tid":545677,"uid":50676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T18:08:33.000Z","msg":"有2個九十幾歲嘅手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07257254599e4fcd01143d22c2cee729107c1923","tid":545677,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T20:30:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cae55a5525a6815ed29479c3c819b597974a94f","tid":545677,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T01:43:06.000Z","msg":"吳壓力?"},{"pid":"ccee5026620f582ff59bfc70464a72aa77e8b88a","tid":545677,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0cae55a5525a6815ed29479c3c819b597974a94f","tid":545677,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T01:43:06.000Z","msg":"吳壓力?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T01:56:38.000Z","msg":"普教中惡果"},{"pid":"7021533560143bc94c966b0ffb3d95af34560093","tid":545677,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T05:12:52.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"d312d8ab63f6c802ea590fbdbfb4812c812bbf5b","tid":545677,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T05:17:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f816dea0e31fb55ca8d3c8ece9fbc42306c5e7cb","tid":545677,"uid":7311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T05:19:45.000Z","msg":"佢啲下一輩有幾多過早死過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95154b07e0fae119f66bff310e8d0db20ba12c09","tid":545677,"uid":8647,"like"